            <seg xml:id="C19_app19-#fThomas_end"/>
               <seg xml:id="C19_app19-#fThomas_start"/>sound which the stranger repeated after them, that she was endeavouring
            to learn their language; and the idea instantly occurred to me, that I should make use
            of the same instructions to the same end. The stranger learned about twenty words at the
            first lesson, most of <seg xml:id="C19_app19-#fThomas_end"/>
            
