            <seg xml:id="C19_app44-#fThomas_end"/>
               <seg xml:id="C19_app44-#fThomas_start"/>And what was I? Of my creation and creator I was absolutely ignorant;
            but I knew that I possessed no money, no friends, no kind of property. I was, besides,
        <seg xml:id="C19_app44-#fThomas_end"/>
            
