            <seg xml:id="C19_app46-#fThomas_end"/>
               <seg xml:id="C19_app46-#fThomas_start"/>with a figure hideously deformed and loathsome; I was not even of the
            same nature as man. I was more agile than they, and could subsist upon coarser diet; I
            bore the extremes of heat and cold with less injury to my frame; my stature far exceeded
        <seg xml:id="C19_app46-#fThomas_end"/>
            
