            <seg xml:id="C19_app48-#fThomas_end"/>
               <seg type="invariant-MissingWit" xml:id="C19_app48-#fThomas_start"/>When I looked around, I saw and heard of none like me. Was I then a
            monster, a blot upon the earth, from which all men fled, and whom all men <seg xml:id="C19_app48-#fThomas_end"/>
            
